[SPEAKER_04] bila je vezana isključivo uz prihode koje firme,

248
00:14:22,240 --> 00:14:24,220
[SPEAKER_04] odnosno hrvatske mikromale srednje,

249
00:14:24,360 --> 00:14:26,600
[SPEAKER_04] pogledaju isključivo njih, uplačuju proračun

250
00:14:26,600 --> 00:14:28,419
[SPEAKER_04] i našli smo da, u biti,

251
00:14:28,419 --> 00:14:30,240
[SPEAKER_04] kad gledate ove koji su ugrožene,

252
00:14:30,240 --> 00:14:32,340
[SPEAKER_04] znači ako propadnu te firme,

253
00:14:32,340 --> 00:14:33,500
[SPEAKER_04] ugroženi su i prihodi,

254
00:14:33,500 --> 00:14:35,940
[SPEAKER_04] pardon, da, prihodi države od

255
00:14:35,940 --> 00:14:37,460
[SPEAKER_04] poreza na dobit, od

256
00:14:37,460 --> 00:14:40,019
[SPEAKER_04] doprinosa i poreza na

257
00:14:40,019 --> 00:14:42,080
[SPEAKER_04] plaće. Čak nismo uračunavali

258
00:14:42,080 --> 00:14:44,320
[SPEAKER_04] PDV, dakle, efekt je vjerojatno još i puno veći,

259
00:14:44,320 --> 00:14:46,200
[SPEAKER_04] jer PDV ovdje nije u računat.

260
00:14:46,200 --> 00:14:48,299
[SPEAKER_04] I vi računajte da isto

261
00:14:48,299 --> 00:14:50,379
[SPEAKER_04] kad bi te firme propale, isto tako

262
00:14:50,379 --> 00:14:52,320
[SPEAKER_04] imali bi ogromnu rupu koju onda ne bi mogli

263
00:14:52,320 --> 00:14:54,240
[SPEAKER_04] financirati ili plaću u jednom sektoru, ili

264
00:14:54,240 --> 00:14:56,340
[SPEAKER_04] mirovine, ili ne znam, hrpu drugih stvari.

265
00:14:56,340 --> 00:14:58,399
[SPEAKER_04] Ono što su mi začunali da kompletan

266
00:14:58,399 --> 00:15:00,340
[SPEAKER_04] segment mikro i malo srednjih

267
00:15:00,340 --> 00:15:02,059
[SPEAKER_04] podzikništva, ono što mi predstavljamo, ono što

268
00:15:02,059 --> 00:15:04,259
[SPEAKER_04] mi, što u biti je stup nekazne ekonomije,

269
00:15:04,259 --> 00:15:05,799
[SPEAKER_04] svake ekonomije, ne samo hrvatske,

270
00:15:05,799 --> 00:15:08,259
[SPEAKER_04] svake u svijetu je uvijek, ono većina

271
00:15:08,259 --> 00:15:09,580
[SPEAKER_04] firme su male, mikro i srednje,

272
00:15:09,580 --> 00:15:12,139
[SPEAKER_04] dakle, one financiraju kompletan trošak plaća

273
00:15:12,139 --> 00:15:14,240
[SPEAKER_04] jednog sektora, financiraju kompletan trošak

274
00:15:14,240 --> 00:15:16,639
[SPEAKER_04] mirovina hrvatskih građana,

275
00:15:16,639 --> 00:15:18,159
[SPEAKER_04] ili ako hoćete, kompletan trošak

276
00:15:18,159 --> 00:15:19,899
[SPEAKER_04] znacinog sustava, vojske,

277
00:15:19,899 --> 00:15:22,500
[SPEAKER_04] policije i tako dalje,

278
00:15:22,500 --> 00:15:23,879
[SPEAKER_04] i tako dalje. Dakle, govorimo o jednom

279
00:15:23,879 --> 00:15:26,240
[SPEAKER_04] važnom segmentu, vlada smatra da

280
00:15:26,240 --> 00:15:28,320
[SPEAKER_04] se male firme srednje mogu gazeti,

281
00:15:28,320 --> 00:15:29,740
[SPEAKER_04] jer ih se nikad, niko ništa,

282
00:15:29,740 --> 00:15:32,559
[SPEAKER_04] za ništa ih se nikad ne pita, sad ih se počelo

283
