[SPEAKER_04] pitati, do sad su imali organizacije

284
00:15:34,440 --> 00:15:36,580
[SPEAKER_04] koji su ih predstavljali, dakle, znamo o kome govorimo,

285
00:15:36,580 --> 00:15:38,940
[SPEAKER_04] HVK-u i HOK-u i tako dalje,

286
00:15:38,940 --> 00:15:40,779
[SPEAKER_04] koji nisu dobili nikakve koristi,

287
00:15:40,779 --> 00:15:42,519
[SPEAKER_04] i sad, konačno, imaju organizaciju

288
00:15:42,519 --> 00:15:44,519
[SPEAKER_04] koji ću se, ono, boriti za njih

289
00:15:44,519 --> 00:15:46,039
[SPEAKER_04] da ovo prežije.

290
00:15:46,039 --> 00:15:50,100
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, to je jedan stvarno,

291
00:15:50,100 --> 00:15:51,980
[SPEAKER_01] zanimljivi su rezultati tog,

292
00:15:51,980 --> 00:15:53,899
[SPEAKER_01] tvojeg VUK-u i istraživanja,

293
00:15:53,899 --> 00:15:56,179
[SPEAKER_01] u kojima se doista vidi koliko je

294
00:15:56,179 --> 00:15:57,919
[SPEAKER_01] bažno malo i srednje poduzetno,

295
00:15:57,919 --> 00:16:00,039
[SPEAKER_01] što i da ne možemo govoriti u kategorijama,

296
00:16:00,039 --> 00:16:02,419
[SPEAKER_01] recimo, ok, netko će

297
00:16:02,419 --> 00:16:04,179
[SPEAKER_01] propasti, netko će preživjeti,

298
00:16:04,179 --> 00:16:06,700
[SPEAKER_01] naravno, upravo taj sektor,

299
00:16:06,700 --> 00:16:08,200
[SPEAKER_01] puni državni proračun

300
00:16:08,200 --> 00:16:09,740
[SPEAKER_01] velikim dijelom,

301
00:16:09,740 --> 00:16:12,419
[SPEAKER_01] i hrani, hrani mnoge.

302
00:16:12,519 --> 00:16:14,059
[SPEAKER_01] Samo da kažem, proste,

303
00:16:14,059 --> 00:16:15,379
[SPEAKER_04] mogu sam reći, znači,

304
00:16:15,379 --> 00:16:16,980
[SPEAKER_04] to isto, to neko će preživjeti,

305
00:16:16,980 --> 00:16:18,759
[SPEAKER_04] neko neće, to isto možete tako

306
00:16:18,759 --> 00:16:20,379
[SPEAKER_04] napraviti pandan sa ljudskim životkima,

307
00:16:20,379 --> 00:16:21,539
[SPEAKER_04] neko će umrijeti, neko neće.

308
00:16:21,539 --> 00:16:23,879
[SPEAKER_04] Poanta je ne dopustiti jedno ni drugo.

309
00:16:23,879 --> 00:16:26,240
[SPEAKER_04] Četio sam danas jedno jako dobro istraživanje

310
00:16:26,240 --> 00:16:28,759
[SPEAKER_04] koje su radili u engleskoj žansljenici,

311
00:16:28,759 --> 00:16:30,200
[SPEAKER_04] koji su ispreživali engleski model

312
00:16:30,200 --> 00:16:32,720
[SPEAKER_04] ovog što su radili

313
00:16:32,720 --> 00:16:34,000
[SPEAKER_04] za pristupa

314
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:35,820
[SPEAKER_04] kovidu sa korejskim.

315
00:16:35,820 --> 00:16:38,419
[SPEAKER_04] Gdje je ta dikotomija između ekonomije

316
00:16:38,419 --> 00:16:40,059
[SPEAKER_04] i života je potpuno lažna.

317
00:16:40,139 --> 00:16:42,220
[SPEAKER_04] to je ono što vlada trenutno bura tliko priče.

318
00:16:42,220 --> 00:16:43,320
[SPEAKER_04] Moramo svi,

319
00:16:43,320 --> 00:16:45,820
[SPEAKER_04] primarne su nam životi,

320
00:16:45,820 --> 00:16:48,759
[SPEAKER_04] ali jedno i drugo zapravo nema razlike.

321
00:16:48,759 --> 00:16:50,679
[SPEAKER_04] Koreja je primjer zemlji

322
00:16:50,679 --> 00:16:51,539
[SPEAKER_04] koja je isto imala,

323
00:16:51,539 --> 00:16:54,580
[SPEAKER_04] oni su identificirali žarišta,

324
00:16:54,580 --> 00:16:56,220
[SPEAKER_04] izolirali su sluče

325
00:16:56,220 --> 00:16:58,179
[SPEAKER_04] od ljude koji su najobroženiji

326
