[SPEAKER_04] da funkcionira normalno.

328
00:17:01,120 --> 00:17:08,500
[SPEAKER_04] To je poanta priče.

329
00:17:08,759 --> 00:17:09,960
[SPEAKER_04] loši mogući odgovor

330
00:17:09,960 --> 00:17:11,200
[SPEAKER_04] na ovu čitavu recensiju.

331
00:17:11,200 --> 00:17:11,759
[SPEAKER_04] Problem je,

332
00:17:11,759 --> 00:17:13,740
[SPEAKER_04] ja se cijelo rime govorim,

333
00:17:13,740 --> 00:17:15,299
[SPEAKER_04] ljudi ako su u strahu

334
00:17:15,299 --> 00:17:16,680
[SPEAKER_04] od samog virusa,

335
00:17:16,680 --> 00:17:17,539
[SPEAKER_04] ako su u strahu

336
00:17:17,539 --> 00:17:20,420
[SPEAKER_04] od čitavog niza faktora,

337
00:17:20,420 --> 00:17:23,299
[SPEAKER_04] neće izlaziti,

338
00:17:23,299 --> 00:17:23,960
[SPEAKER_04] neće se družiti,

339
00:17:23,960 --> 00:17:24,559
[SPEAKER_04] neće se okupiti.

340
00:17:24,559 --> 00:17:25,319
[SPEAKER_04] Da, jedan dio hoće,

